      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CREEPING TIGER (3) is a promising dog in the frame at five of 10 starts including four wins and was in the minors again latest (22.66) over 400m at Bulli. Has never missed the frame at the trip from seven starts. Happy to have him on top this line-up. DOMINEERING (6) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 8 last run (23.07) at this track. Yet to taste defeat from two runs out of this box. Expected to be in this for a long way. GRAVEL DUST (4) impressed when clocking a swift 18.20 over 320m at this track three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Top win three back and rates a key player again. SHADOW DASH (1) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
